  <p>Hi, 50mm is my happy place.  I'm {{ site.author.firstName }} {{ site.author.lastName}}. This static website acts as a compendium of images I've taken over the years.  Github template + Cloudfare hosting + some vibe coding tweaks with Cursor.</p>
  <p>Born in Europe, 30 years in Japan. Camera Enthusiast (Canon R6, 50mm 1.4, 70-200mm 2.8, 100mm 2.8). Martial arts enthusiast (BJJ Coach at Strapple and Carpe Diem), Semi-retired MBA (Managing a VC-company's retreat from Japan), Trilingual French-English-Japanese. Bike enthusiast (Ducati Monster 696).</p>
  
  <p>Palette: 
